title: WALKOUT RAMBLER WITH FULLY FANCED YARD IN HIGH DEMAND EDINA
posting_body: ['This Edina Rambler style Duplex located on gorgeous 0.4 acre wooded lot.', 'Prestigious Edina school district.', 'Lower Level of the property has walkout to the private, fully enclosed by the fence backyard.', 'One block from Lake Pamela and Pamela Park.', 'Property features 3 Bedrooms and 1 Full and 1 Half Baths.', 'Over 1600 finished sq.', 'feet on upper and lower levels.', 'Upper level fully covered with hardwood floors and bathroom has tiled floor and walls.', 'All appliances included - Cooktop, Dishwasher, Disposal, Range, Refrigerator, Wall Oven, Washer, Dryer.', '1 car attached garage with door opener.', 'Central A/C. Only half mile to Southdale Shopping Center.', 'Monthly Rent: $1825', 'Security Deposit: $1825', 'Tenants Pay All Utilities', 'Tenants are responsible for lawn care and snow removal.', 'Pet Policy - Some Pets are accepted with additional rent & deposit', 'Dogs Must be 20 Pounds or Less when Fully Grown.', 'Cats Must be Neutered or Spayed.', 'No Puppies or Kittens Please.', 'MUST HAVE A POSITIVE VERIFIABLE RENTAL HISTORY', 'This Property is not Section 8 Certified.', 'PLEASE INCLUDE YOUR CONTACT INFORMATION when email with questions or to schedule a showing', 'This Advertisement will be Removed as soon as Property will be Rented.', 'Neighboring Cities - Bloomington, Eden Prairie, Minnetonka, Hopkins, St. Louis Park, Minneapolis, Richfield', 'All information is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed and should be independently verified.', 'Real estate advertised herein is subject to the US Federal Fair Housing Act of 1968, which makes it illegal to make or publish any advertisement that indicates any preference, limitation, or discrimination based on race, color, religion, sex, handicap, familial status, or national origin.']
